### Register User

POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Puish",
  "email": "puish@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login User

POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "puish@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Protected Route

GET http://localhost:5000/api/protected
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN